data.title: Fresh  Pandesal
data.text:
Always get the fresh pan de sal.  The even have it on wheat.  Located in a small plaza next to Seafood City, Jolibee and Red Ribbon.  Be careful, since most older Filipino drivers don't pay attention.  

If you are craving for Filipino baked good, come here they have everything you could think of.  My favorites are pan de sal and the ensaymada.  Service is good.  And price decent.

data.title: Valerio's CA
data.text: One of of my favorite Filipino bakeries.... it takes you back to that warm fuzzy feeling, just add a good cup of joe!
